''Determine and set up Skirmish Mission:'' The player with initiative shuffles his deck of Skirmish Mission cards and draws one card. This card lists the name of the mission, which map it is played on, and the special rules for the mission.<p>
After drawing this card, players refer to the matching skirmish mission’s diagram, and then build the map and place tokens on it as shown.

* Player’s place only the “A” or “B” tokens on the map that match the Skirmish Mission card’s letter.